ltList"><li data-li-identifier="d)" data-name="d)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">d)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">humane veksthormonpreparater</article></article></li></ul></article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">Merknaden til punkt 6 endres til:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/" id="ledd-2">Til litra a – d, i stedet for som nå: Til litra a – c.</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/3/" id="ledd-3">Endringen trer i kraft straks.</article></main></body></html>